    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure provided in the <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api__settings__mgmt_1gga1711bc9f45a8114a6b0c89db4a40e3dea65c675aa2e807d9977a5ff13a97c75a0" kindref="member">MGMT_EVT_OP_SETTINGS_MGMT_ACCESS</ref> notification callback. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This callback function is used to notify the application about a pending setting read/write/delete/load/save/commit request and to authorise or deny it. Access will be allowed so long as no handlers return an error, if one returns an error then access will be denied. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
